title: Bug 109350: Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
description: The output parameter is not being displayed in the data set dialog.
OB: The output parameter is not visible in the data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Call the stored procedure from Oracle database.
2. Verify that the query result is stored in an output parameter as an object.
3. Open the data set dialog.
4. Check if the output parameter is displayed in the dialog.
